description: Las Vegas’ First WING TRUCK.  A Southern Boy and Girl’s Dream is becoming a reality.  Wings and Tenders made with Southern Love and dressed up with Flavor and Spice.  Fresh and Never Frozen.. Fresh Cut French Fries, Fried Pickles, and a bunch of other things to tickle your tastebuds. We hope you will join us as we fulfill our dream of having our own restaurant on wheels. We look forward to serving you:)  OHHHH and WHAT?? A DESSERT WING…TRY IT! YOU’LL NEVER BELIEVE YOUR TASTE BUDS…
name: Sin City Wings
